<p begin="100500000t" end="106800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>左手!</b></font></p>
<p begin="121200000t" end="129000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還在…</b></font></p>
<p begin="142600000t" end="158000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>又回歸了</b></font></p>
<p begin="165600000t" end="195400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不  應該說還好能回歸嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="236300000t" end="254000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>抱歉  早安</b></font></p>
<p begin="288200000t" end="309300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>果然她們都忘記了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="335000000t" end="353400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>給你們添麻煩了</b></font></p>
<p begin="355200000t" end="374000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>萊月昴再次啟動</b></font></p>
<p begin="392700000t" end="420100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>話說  今天幾號現在幾點?</b></font></p>
<p begin="537400000t" end="588700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>自分の過去に囚われ迷って</b></font></p>
<p begin="537400000t" end="588700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}無法擺脫自己過去的束縛  迷失了前進方向</b></font></p>
<p begin="589100000t" end="638700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>そうじゃないよと　言い聞かせて　全てを</b></font></p>
<p begin="589100000t" end="638700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}還自欺述說那並不是全部</b></font></p>
<p begin="639100000t" end="689600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>自由に操れるかなんて</b></font></p>
<p begin="639100000t" end="689600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}不知道這些是否能自由控制</b></font></p>
<p begin="690400000t" end="714600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>分からないよと　空は霞んで</b></font></p>
<p begin="690400000t" end="714600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}天色為何又如此朦朧</b></font></p>
<p begin="715400000t" end="739200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>正解はどこ</b></font></p>
<p begin="715400000t" end="739200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}答案又在何處</b></font></p>
<p begin="740500000t" end="791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>僕の手のひらに　残る大事なもの</b></font></p>
<p begin="740500000t" end="791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}雙手還殘留著有什麼很重要的事尚未完成的感覺</b></font></p>
<p begin="792200000t" end="840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>忘れない記憶　何度でも</b></font></p>
<p begin="792200000t" end="840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}這段記憶將塵封於心  永久保存</b></font></p>
<p begin="840600000t" end="891900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>君を守り抜くと叫んで</b></font></p>
<p begin="840600000t" end="891900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}誓要將你保護到底的決心已化作言語放聲吶喊</b></font></p>
<p begin="894400000t" end="941900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>巻き戻しの中　掴んだ愛は　そう</b></font></p>
<p begin="894400000t" end="941900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}回放逝去的倒帶  把對你永恆的摯愛捧在心中</b></font></p>
<p begin="943200000t" end="965300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>離しはしないから</b></font></p>
<p begin="943200000t" end="965300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}定不會輕易放手</b></font></p>
<p begin="966900000t" end="1018200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>散りばめた想い　今一度きりの願いへ</b></font></p>
<p begin="966900000t" end="1018200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}這是最後一次請求  將這散落一地的思念</b></font></p>
<p begin="977800000t" end="978200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正兰亭粗黑_GBK" size="70" color="#a098ce"><b><font face="方正小标宋_GBK"><font size="3">D</font>mg</font></b></font><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b><font color="#bebdc4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK">:</font></font></b></font><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b><font color="#bebdc4">        <font face="方正小标宋_GBK">國<br />\h\h\h\h\h<font face="方正兰亭粗黑_GBK">        <font face="方正小标宋_GBK"></font>組</font></font></font></b></font></p>
