<p begin="979000000t" end="1017400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正兰亭粗黑_GBK" size="70" color="#a098ce"><b><font color="#000000"></font>幕</b></font></p>
<p begin="979000000t" end="1017400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正兰亭粗黑_GBK" size="70" color="#a098ce"><b><font face="方正小标宋_GBK"><font color="#000000"><font size="35">dmguo.org</font></font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="1019900000t" end="1067900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>次への僕に　託したよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1019900000t" end="1067900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}託付給未來的自己</b></font></p>
<p begin="1068300000t" end="1119200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>いつかの約束　光の道しるべになる</b></font></p>
<p begin="1068300000t" end="1119200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}曾經的約定  化作黎明的燈塔指引我前進</b></font></p>
<p begin="1119200000t" end="1229700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>誓いをさあ　君のため　最期まで</b></font></p>
<p begin="1119200000t" end="1229700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}我發誓將為了你支撐到最後一刻</b></font></p>
<p begin="1231800000t" end="1280600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>涙さえ力に変えてきっと　描いていた望む未来へ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1231800000t" end="1280600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}連淚水也化作力量  一定會將心中描繪的所期待的未來</b></font></p>
<p begin="1282700000t" end="1307290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>繋ぐよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1282700000t" end="1307290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}與現實銜接</b></font></p>
<p begin="1341300000t" end="1365300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>第三次的羅茲瓦爾宅邸的第一天</b></font></p>
<p begin="1378200000t" end="1388700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那股寒氣</b></font></p>
<p begin="1394100000t" end="1427000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>最開始的死因是在睡覺中的衰弱致死嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="1436400000t" end="1448000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是第二次是…</b></font></p>
<p begin="1457300000t" end="1472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有人襲擊我</b></font></p>
<p begin="1485000000t" end="1532500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我被幹掉了  也就是說宅邸上的人也是目標嗎?</b></font></p>
<p begin="1543200000t" end="1574800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>和贓物庫那時一樣  與愛蜜莉雅的王選競爭有關聯</b></font></p>
<p begin="1583200000t" end="1597500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是  就算知道這些</b></font></p>
<p begin="1597500000t" end="1643000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我都缺乏有說服力的證據  和預防的手段</b></font></p>
<p begin="1649000000t" end="1675000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>而且兇手的面貌以及武器都沒有看到</b></font></p>
<p begin="1676500000t" end="1693900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這不是完全白死了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="1695300000t" end="1712300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>簡直煩得要命</b></font></p>
<p begin="1712900000t" end="1743200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你想立刻打住或者被我打飛  選一個吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="1749900000t" end="1762300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>抱歉  抱歉</b></font></p>
<p begin="1766300000t" end="1803800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是這樣繞圈  很神奇的是頭腦也能轉得快</b></font></p>
<p begin="1809100000t" end="1830200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你就體諒一下吧  畢竟我們關係那麼好</b></font></p>
<p begin="1834300000t" end="1863700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>碧蒂和你有什麼關係嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="1866500000t" end="1884700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我們只見了兩次面而已</b></font></p>
<p begin="1919500000t" end="1943200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我不會給你添麻煩的</b></font></p>
<p begin="1946600000t" end="1966400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不如把茶端出來  讓我好好享受一下</b></font></p>
<p begin="1968500000t" end="1990000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我怎麼可能為你端出來</b></font></p>
<p begin="1997500000t" end="2015600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真是煩死了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2021300000t" end="2039300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你在看什麼書</b></font></p>
<p begin="2043500000t" end="2077300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不知道書裡面有沒有寫著  怎麼趕走闖入房間的蟲子</b></font></p>
<p begin="2081900000t" end="2117800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有蟲子跑進書庫裡了嗎  那真是太糟糕了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2120300000t" end="2129600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是什麼樣的蟲子</b></font></p>
<p begin="2136800000t" end="2158600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你差不多可以出去了吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="2162300000t" end="2177000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>手的顫抖也已經停止</b></font></p>
<p begin="2178900000t" end="2204800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>現在已經足夠掩飾掉你的恐懼了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2207400000t" end="2221200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>暴露了嗎?</b></font></p>
<p begin="2224900000t" end="2242000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>難道你還想隱瞞嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="2244700000t" end="2273300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒認識多久就被你隨意利用  真讓人意外</b></font></p>
<p begin="2280300000t" end="2299300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真是一點都不溫柔</b></font></p>
<p begin="2303600000t" end="2314200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過得救了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2318800000t" end="2325100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>下次也拜託你了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2333200000t" end="2351100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>被你拜託  我也只會感到困擾</b></font></p>
<p begin="2355600000t" end="2374200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以不要再來了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2383800000t" end="2390900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>去  去</b></font></p>
<p begin="2400400000t" end="2416300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還叫去去…</b></font></p>
<p begin="2426700000t" end="2450500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>難道剛在說的蟲子就是我嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="2452600000t" end="2474200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>夠了  趕快出去</b></font></p>
<p begin="2557900000t" end="2583390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒有花壇的話  就是直接沒命了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2587400000t" end="2595600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那個…</b></font></p>
<p begin="2613390000t" end="2633600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>能問一下你還好嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="2643200000t" end="2657800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭</b></font></p>
<p begin="2660500000t" end="2688700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>只有你的那份溫柔才能治癒我</b></font></p>
<p begin="2688700000t" end="2733700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那個花壇  雷姆昨天剛用動物的糞便施肥過</b></font></p>
<p begin="2749700000t" end="2755900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>三秒規則</b></font></p>
<p begin="2759700000t" end="2778900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>無效  應該無效吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="2787400000t" end="2806900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這種叫做狗屎運吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="2808900000t" end="2834700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>可以想成是幸運加身呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="2846200000t" end="2879000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭已經轉換成安慰模式了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2905600000t" end="2918000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>帕克  醒一醒</b></font></p>
<p begin="2980100000t" end="2997400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>早安  莉雅</b></font></p>
<p begin="3000500000t" end="3012100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>早安  帕克</b></font></p>
<p begin="3020400000t" end="3036400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然你才剛睡醒  就突然拜託你</b></font></p>
<p begin="3037800000t" end="3059400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>能不能幫昴的身體沖洗一下</b></font></p>
<p begin="3064700000t" end="3073000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴?</b></font></p>
<p begin="3092100000t" end="3107700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼就開始洗了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3110800000t" end="3117100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看招</b></font></p>
<p begin="3179400000t" end="3192600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看  變乾淨了吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3195400000t" end="3203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>太好了呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="3258000000t" end="3275900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我都以為要死了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3280700000t" end="3301100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒有別的做法了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="3302100000t" end="3317300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>怎麼感覺你好像很開心啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="3329000000t" end="3353200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒有這種事</b></font></p>
<p begin="3365500000t" end="3383300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>回敬貓拳</b></font></p>
<p begin="3395200000t" end="3413100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>幹得不錯啊  看招</b></font></p>
<p begin="3418500000t" end="3449100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我這招必殺技如何  貓哭撓癢癢</b></font></p>
<p begin="3450900000t" end="3463700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>住手</b></font></p>
<p begin="3466400000t" end="3480400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>尾巴拳</b></font></p>
<p begin="3480400000t" end="3483900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你這…</b></font></p>
<p begin="3484500000t" end="3508300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>接著是肉球踩踏</b></font></p>
<p begin="3577500000t" end="3588700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真的抱歉  我不行了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3591100000t" end="3604300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你們兩個在幹什麼呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="3618500000t" end="3625400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我肚子都痛了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3628000000t" end="3639000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>討厭  要死了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3680700000t" end="3707000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>總之  挽回了最初不好的印象</b></font></p>
<p begin="3710800000t" end="3727500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>多謝您的助攻  岳父</b></font></p>
<p begin="3729300000t" end="3743500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>誰是你的岳父</b></font></p>
<p begin="3746100000t" end="3766000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我決不會輕易把女兒交給你</b></font></p>
<p begin="3770800000t" end="3795100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不要說了  你們都太搞笑了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3805800000t" end="3824500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>莉雅的笑容是最棒的</b></font></p>
<p begin="3830600000t" end="3847200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴你也這麼想的對吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3851100000t" end="3864500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>超·贊同</b></font></p>
<p begin="3879100000t" end="3916800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭的笑容  對我而言便是最耀眼的翠星</b></font></p>
<p begin="3921300000t" end="3936300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真是的  連昴也這樣</b></font></p>
<p begin="3943800000t" end="3960700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還有那個「炭」是什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="3964700000t" end="3974900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是從哪裡來的</b></font></p>
<p begin="3993000000t" end="4016200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這便是所謂的愛稱</b></font></p>
<p begin="4020300000t" end="4044500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就像帕克稱愛蜜莉雅炭為莉雅一樣</b></font></p>
<p begin="4046700000t" end="4079900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是一種表示兩人間親密關係的愛情體現</b></font></p>
<p begin="4087800000t" end="4127000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我不記得和昴的關係有那麼好</b></font></p>
<p begin="4137200000t" end="4168600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然是暴擊的普通發言  但我不會氣餒</b></font></p>
<p begin="4174700000t" end="4194400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就當是今後關係的預支吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="4197300000t" end="4234200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我想和你親近到能用愛稱稱呼的關係</b></font></p>
<p begin="4237800000t" end="4243000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>OK?</b></font></p>
<p begin="4283500000t" end="4301300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯  我知道了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4305500000t" end="4322200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這麼說我就能理解了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4343900000t" end="4360600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>討厭  不要看這邊</b></font></p>
<p begin="4369300000t" end="4398300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還想著會不會被討厭  看樣子感覺還不錯</b></font></p>
<p begin="4409200000t" end="4424800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>怎麼回事  帕克解說員</b></font></p>
<p begin="4430000000t" end="4450100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我家女兒的朋友很少　</b></font></p>
<p begin="4453100000t" end="4482700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以一直都渴望這種愛稱  因此很容易泡到手</b></font></p>
<p begin="4487600000t" end="4506700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>原來我的女主角很容易泡到手</b></font></p>
<p begin="4512400000t" end="4523100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>姐姐  姐姐</b></font></p>
<p begin="4525600000t" end="4557500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一會不見  客人就變成落湯雞了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4562100000t" end="4569300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雷姆  雷姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="4573800000t" end="4607000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一會不見  客人就變成了骯髒的破抹布</b></font></p>
<p begin="4610700000t" end="4643900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不說我也知道自己變成下水道的老鼠</b></font></p>
<p begin="4648800000t" end="4679900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>主人  羅茲瓦爾大人回來了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4685000000t" end="4695900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>請到宅邸</b></font></p>
<p begin="4717900000t" end="4726800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>來了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4731000000t" end="4753400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>第三次的初次會面活動</b></font></p>
<p begin="4767900000t" end="4783700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>目前掌握到的情報是</b></font></p>
<p begin="4787000000t" end="4819400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>第四天晚上會有某人來襲擊</b></font></p>
<p begin="4826600000t" end="4849100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果能把這件事告訴羅茲瓦爾他們就好</b></font></p>
<p begin="4854200000t" end="4877500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過我又沒法說明情報的來源</b></font></p>
<p begin="4881700000t" end="4907000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>弄不好的話  還可能被懷疑成是刺客的同夥</b></font></p>
<p begin="4912600000t" end="4954900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>至少如果能弄清楚襲擊者的身形  就另當別論了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4963000000t" end="4999500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以從這次起四天期間  我會徹底收集情報</b></font></p>
<p begin="5001500000t" end="5021200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一定要揭露襲擊者的真面目</b></font></p>
<p begin="5030000000t" end="5040600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>為此…</b></font></p>
<p begin="5047700000t" end="5065000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>獎賞就如你所願</b></font></p>
<p begin="5071000000t" end="5106100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好了  儘管說出你的願望吧</b></font></p>
