<p begin="8180200000t" end="8198400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯  果然很難喝</b></font></p>
<p begin="8203800000t" end="8241800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這是宅邸最高級的茶葉  你這感謝肯定會遭天譴</b></font></p>
<p begin="8258400000t" end="8282900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>居然在客人的面前明目張膽地偷懶</b></font></p>
<p begin="8286700000t" end="8310400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我真是對你的膽大包天無言以對了</b></font></p>
<p begin="8314200000t" end="8347200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是客人先提出讓我不用那麼拘泥的</b></font></p>
<p begin="8352400000t" end="8370000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>拉姆只是照您的吩咐而已</b></font></p>
<p begin="8383400000t" end="8403500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>然後  學習進展得還順利嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="8407200000t" end="8414600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>算是吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="8420900000t" end="8444200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>已經能夠看懂這樣的童話了</b></font></p>
<p begin="8452100000t" end="8483600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在書上能享受到常識之間微妙的差距  很有趣</b></font></p>
<p begin="8488600000t" end="8508900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>正所謂異文化交流的感覺</b></font></p>
<p begin="8516400000t" end="8548100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我也引進一些自己老家的童話吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="8552000000t" end="8566100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>「哭泣的赤鬼」之類的</b></font></p>
<p begin="8597000000t" end="8608900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>哭泣的赤鬼?</b></font></p>
<p begin="8625700000t" end="8640900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>要不要說給你聽?</b></font></p>
<p begin="8676800000t" end="8695000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼就請你洗耳恭聽吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="8705300000t" end="8715800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>很久很久以前</b></font></p>
<p begin="8719200000t" end="8759000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有一個地方住著赤鬼和青鬼</b></font></p>
<p begin="8770300000t" end="8796000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>他們是非常要好的朋友</b></font></p>
<p begin="8808100000t" end="8845900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>赤鬼想和村裡的人和睦相處</b></font></p>
<p begin="8857700000t" end="8888200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是人們卻害怕著不敢冒然接近</b></font></p>
<p begin="8897100000t" end="8941400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>無法坐視不管的青鬼  為了赤鬼想到了某項計劃</b></font></p>
<p begin="8950300000t" end="8988000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我會在村子大鬧  赤鬼你就來阻止我吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="8994100000t" end="9023100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這樣一來村裡的人一定會相信你的</b></font></p>
<p begin="9035500000t" end="9074100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>計劃成功  赤鬼和人類們和睦相處了</b></font></p>
<p begin="9083100000t" end="9120800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是隨著時間的流逝  赤鬼開始在意起某件事</b></font></p>
<p begin="9132100000t" end="9169500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>他在意的是  從那天開始再也沒來找自己的青鬼</b></font></p>
<p begin="9182600000t" end="9215500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>某天  赤鬼去了青鬼的家</b></font></p>
<p begin="9222500000t" end="9262700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>然而卻發現大門鎖緊  門上並貼著一張紙</b></font></p>
<p begin="9274700000t" end="9292800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那張紙上這樣寫著</b></font></p>
<p begin="9303800000t" end="9348000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>赤鬼  請你和人類們和睦相處  快樂地生活下去吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="9358600000t" end="9382600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果我繼續和你來往的話</b></font></p>
<p begin="9388300000t" end="9416300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你可能也會被當作惡鬼</b></font></p>
<p begin="9427800000t" end="9453500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>於是我決定出外旅行了</b></font></p>
<p begin="9461000000t" end="9490000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是我永遠都不會忘記你的</b></font></p>
<p begin="9497400000t" end="9525000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>再見了  請保重身體</b></font></p>
<p begin="9532900000t" end="9564900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你永遠的朋友  青鬼筆</b></font></p>
<p begin="9591600000t" end="9617800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>赤鬼沉默著看了一遍又一遍</b></font></p>
<p begin="9628200000t" end="9652200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>抽泣著  留下了眼淚</b></font></p>
<p begin="9661900000t" end="9667600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>完</b></font></p>
<p begin="9690600000t" end="9703300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真是個悲傷的故事</b></font></p>
<p begin="9711300000t" end="9761100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是啊  不過我覺得這也是個溫柔的故事</b></font></p>
<p begin="9769000000t" end="9804000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>拉姆認為登場人物都是笨蛋</b></font></p>
<p begin="9812900000t" end="9837300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>無論赤鬼  青鬼還是村民們</b></font></p>
<p begin="9842100000t" end="9867400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這還真是個毫不留情的感想</b></font></p>
<p begin="9874800000t" end="9893800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然我也不否定</b></font></p>
<p begin="9898400000t" end="9933900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以我對這個故事又愛又恨</b></font></p>
<p begin="9947400000t" end="9974800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然青鬼的自我犧牲很帥氣</b></font></p>
<p begin="9979200000t" end="9996700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但也毫無回報  非常地傻</b></font></p>
<p begin="10003900000t" end="10032400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>而且我是期待有付出就有收穫的人</b></font></p>
<p begin="10040800000t" end="10061000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人是這麼看青鬼的嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="10076800000t" end="10102000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但拉姆認為赤鬼更無可救藥</b></font></p>
<p begin="10112700000t" end="10133400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>把青鬼捲入自己的願望中來</b></font></p>
<p begin="10136500000t" end="10175400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>結果到最後只是失去了青鬼  自己卻毫無損失</b></font></p>
<p begin="10182000000t" end="10217400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那你覺得這兩個鬼該怎麼做</b></font></p>
<p begin="10226200000t" end="10255500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果赤鬼真想和人類友好相處</b></font></p>
<p begin="10260400000t" end="10282100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>折斷自己的角和人類一起住就好了</b></font></p>
<p begin="10295000000t" end="10312600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在青鬼看不下去之前</b></font></p>
<p begin="10318290000t" end="10328290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就該痛下決心</b></font></p>
<p begin="10335400000t" end="10369000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你這意見還真是極端</b></font></p>
<p begin="10373290000t" end="10380200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="10387500000t" end="10420990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那客人想跟兩個鬼中的哪一個和睦相處呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="10426090000t" end="10436600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>哪一個?</b></font></p>
<p begin="10461500000t" end="10489000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>滿腦理想  只會讓別人替自己善後的赤鬼</b></font></p>
<p begin="10496500000t" end="10516800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>和沉浸在自我犧牲之中的笨蛋青鬼</b></font></p>
<p begin="10629200000t" end="10639900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真是無聊的回答</b></font></p>
<p begin="10653800000t" end="10670400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>居然想和兩個鬼都和睦相處</b></font></p>
<p begin="10676000000t" end="10696600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人還真是優柔寡斷的花心鬼呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="10703500000t" end="10714700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>總有一天你會後悔的</b></font></p>
<p begin="10716700000t" end="10746700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我記得我們說的不是這種事吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="10755400000t" end="10778300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>先不討論客人故鄉的童話故事</b></font></p>
<p begin="10783700000t" end="10804900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你對這邊的童話印象最深的是?</b></font></p>
<p begin="10810100000t" end="10822600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這麼一說</b></font></p>
<p begin="10827800000t" end="10841300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>比較在意的果然還是…</b></font></p>
<p begin="10842000000t" end="10882800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>中間這篇龍的故事和卷尾的魔女的故事</b></font></p>
<p begin="10891400000t" end="10927800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我終於知道親龍王國魯格尼卡這個名字的由來了</b></font></p>
<p begin="10931700000t" end="10935700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="10943100000t" end="10966800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>裡面寫了王族和龍的盟約</b></font></p>
<p begin="10971700000t" end="10999400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>與其說是童話  更像是歷史故事啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11004400000t" end="11021500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是的  因為這是事實</b></font></p>
<p begin="11032000000t" end="11098700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如今高貴的龍仍在遠方的大瀑布守護著這個國家</b></font></p>
<p begin="11109100000t" end="11142000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一直到與皇族訂下的誓約達成為止</b></font></p>
<p begin="11150100000t" end="11195000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>等等  與龍訂下誓約的一族不是前陣子滅亡了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="11201400000t" end="11218700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是的  很簡單就滅絕了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11228200000t" end="11252600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>龍的要求也無人知曉</b></font></p>
<p begin="11262800000t" end="11293200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如今的狀況下龍會有何動作  只有神…</b></font></p>
<p begin="11301400000t" end="11331500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不  只有龍才知道了  客人</b></font></p>
<p begin="11356400000t" end="11363600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>對了  拉姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="11368400000t" end="11381800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這個魔女的故事…</b></font></p>
<p begin="11381800000t" end="11393900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我不想談這個故事</b></font></p>
<p begin="11407400000t" end="11417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我待太久了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11425700000t" end="11454300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人  晚餐時我會再來告知您</b></font></p>
<p begin="11478100000t" end="11489300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯…</b></font></p>
<p begin="11501800000t" end="11527600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>剛才的故事  兩個鬼的</b></font></p>
<p begin="11531200000t" end="11545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>請不要講給雷姆聽</b></font></p>
<p begin="11549500000t" end="11567800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那孩子肯定不會喜歡的</b></font></p>
<p begin="11657000000t" end="11682500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>可怕的魔女  恐懼的魔女</b></font></p>
<p begin="11689900000t" end="11713000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就連直呼其名都令人畏懼</b></font></p>
<p begin="11721100000t" end="11740100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>人們稱呼她為…</b></font></p>
<p begin="11749200000t" end="11762600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>「嫉妒魔女」</b></font></p>
<p begin="11821900000t" end="11832400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真的不要緊嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="11835800000t" end="11861700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我可以幫你叫龍車送你到王都的</b></font></p>
<p begin="11864200000t" end="11879200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>都說了不用</b></font></p>
<p begin="11885000000t" end="11929800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>等我成為強大聰慧的有錢人  能配得上愛蜜莉雅炭時</b></font></p>
<p begin="11934300000t" end="11951900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我會騎著白馬回來帶走你的</b></font></p>
<p begin="11955000000t" end="11988000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>帶手絹了嗎  還有飲用水和拉格馬特礦石都帶好了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="11988100000t" end="12014700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還有你一個人睡得著嗎  不會怕寂寞吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="12015800000t" end="12029400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>完全變成老媽模式了!</b></font></p>
<p begin="12031300000t" end="12059300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼昴再會了  保重</b></font></p>
<p begin="12064000000t" end="12082900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不要弄丟我送你的禮物</b></font></p>
<p begin="12088400000t" end="12127400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我們畢竟共處了三天  所以我多加了那麼點禮物</b></font></p>
<p begin="12147300000t" end="12171200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>封口費吧  我知道了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12175100000t" end="12200100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我不會多嘴  對龍起誓</b></font></p>
<p begin="12203600000t" end="12242400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>跟你相處之後  感覺對你用陰謀詭計都是多餘</b></font></p>
<p begin="12251800000t" end="12296400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>另外在這個國家對龍起誓  可是最高級的起誓</b></font></p>
<p begin="12303500000t" end="12323600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>請務必牢記</b></font></p>
<p begin="12329600000t" end="12337400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>明白</b></font></p>
<p begin="12344200000t" end="12360100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我也受了你們兩人不少照顧</b></font></p>
<p begin="12367500000t" end="12392400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>特別是雷姆琳  謝謝你每天美味的飯菜</b></font></p>
<p begin="12399800000t" end="12414500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>拉姆親的話…</b></font></p>
<p begin="12415400000t" end="12440900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯  打掃廁所什麼的很在行呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="12445000000t" end="12487400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>姐姐姐姐  客人的恭維話差到令人絕望呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="12489200000t" end="12524800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雷姆雷姆  客人的恭維話致命地沒品呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="12524800000t" end="12551400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>吵死了  我是真想不出什麼好的!</b></font></p>
<p begin="12568000000t" end="12581900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過還是多謝你們</b></font></p>
<p begin="12588600000t" end="12592200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯</b></font></p>
<p begin="12667400000t" end="12703100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴  謝謝你幫我那麼多</b></font></p>
<p begin="12708600000t" end="12726900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果你有什麼事  隨時都可以來找我</b></font></p>
<p begin="12743700000t" end="12747400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯</b></font></p>
<p begin="12776000000t" end="12798300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭  謝謝你</b></font></p>
<p begin="13006700000t" end="13020700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好了  就選這裡了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13028800000t" end="13048700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在這能清楚地看到愛蜜莉雅的房間</b></font></p>
<p begin="13059700000t" end="13091200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>然後只需靜待事件發生</b></font></p>
<p begin="13105300000t" end="13113400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>並出面阻止</b></font></p>
<p begin="13146900000t" end="13176900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>要是讓她們知道我拿它來幹這些  肯定會被罵的吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="13194400000t" end="13208000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真想被她們罵啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="13233000000t" end="13248400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真不想死啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="13273700000t" end="13288000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>也不想讓大家死</b></font></p>
<p begin="13311600000t" end="13352900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="35">{\an8}本字幕由動漫國字幕組製作(dmguo.org)<br />僅供試看,請支持購買正版音像製品</font></p>
<p begin="13325700000t" end="13347800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我應該說過吧  菜月昴</b></font></p>
<p begin="13354900000t" end="13387600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>每次回歸時  就算所有人都忘記了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13363300000t" end="13401300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="35">{\an8}翻譯:Ino17&小勳&我不是小呆   校對:初夏   時軸:秋穗姬   後期&MKV:小聖   特效:鎖定</font></p>
<p begin="13394100000t" end="13411500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你也要銘記於心</b></font></p>
<p begin="13460000000t" end="13493000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>說起來  這次雷姆沒有出去購物呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="13504700000t" end="13526500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是沒必要因為多我一個而特地去買嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13547500000t" end="13567300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>離天黑還有一段時間</b></font></p>
<p begin="13573900000t" end="13590100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>集中注意</b></font></p>
<p begin="13718200000t" end="13730200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>緊急逃脫</b></font></p>
<p begin="13743300000t" end="13747200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看到了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13751500000t" end="13761500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我看到了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13766800000t" end="13780900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>鎖鏈聲的真實身份</b></font></p>
<p begin="13789900000t" end="13807300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過對方居然追過來了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13855900000t" end="13896200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>完全被對方玩弄於掌中了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13964300000t" end="13979500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>放馬過來吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="14050800000t" end="14079900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我可是充滿鬥志</b></font></p>
<p begin="14120200000t" end="14144000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>現出你的真身吧  混蛋</b></font></p>
<p begin="14146800000t" end="14174800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>為了見你一面  我可是費勁千辛萬苦</b></font></p>
<p begin="14332000000t" end="14343600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真沒辦法</b></font></p>
<p begin="14443100000t" end="14484400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>明明在毫不知情的情況下被終結  才是最好的結局</b></font></p>
<p begin="14540100000t" end="14549300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>騙人的吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="14561700000t" end="14566400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雷姆…</b></font></p>
